      %p
        %strong ·High purity
      %p The physical purity is greater than 99% as determined by SDS-PAGE.
      %p
        %strong ·Low bacterial DNA contamination
      %p A bacterial TaqMan qPCR assay targeting 16S rRNA was performed with at least 5 ul BioGeek<sup>TM</sup> T4 DNA Ligase as a template. The level of DNA contamination in BioGeek<sup>TM</sup> T4 DNA Ligase has been estimated at less than 10 genome equivalents of bacterial DNA per unit of the enzyme.
      %p
        %strong ·High efficiency
      %p T4 DNA Ligase catalyzes the ligation of sticky or blunt end DNA fragments in only 5 minutes at room temperature
